{"tid":244595,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我有十億，一定訓身買起譚仔","createTime":"2017-05-15T14:19:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T14:35:26.000Z","uid":78512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8a595b48cc76682aeecd5d180ec5b5808e0db564","tid":244595,"uid":78512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:19:01.000Z","msg":"丸龜製麵在通告中披露，截至去年3月底，譚仔全年收入為6.9億元（107.6億日圓），純利約9,600萬港元（14.9億日圓），按年增長22%，成績媲美上市公司。<br />\n<br />\nAcquisition pricing model:<br />\n<br />\n收購價：十億港元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n純利：約9,600萬港元<br />\n預期資本回報率為9.6%（未扣除攤銷、利息，及收購費用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n人民幣50萬做一年定期，都係得4%息，譚仔接近10%息真是無得輸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再比較同類公司的估值<br />\n大家樂（0341）PE：~30x<br />\n大快活（052）PE：20x<br />\n譚仔PE：10x <br />\n換句話説譚仔的估值比大家樂平3倍，比大快活平2倍。轟呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n再講丸龜製麵本身進入亞洲市場。要以香港作爲起點的話，以收購譚仔獲得其店舖管理和對本土市場的認識，是好make sense的決定。<br />\n<br />\n小二，一個大倭寇雞翼唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea8207d120d879fb8e106cec99ebe6787c33f70","tid":244595,"uid":58914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:19:49.000Z","msg":"咁三哥呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf5374cdc974a7a0a6b2321ccf9321774599247e","tid":244595,"uid":78512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:25:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁三哥呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔夠資料，答你唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f204c3a1798f00be68d428413ae7c190ee47251","tid":244595,"uid":60615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T14:29:39.000Z","msg":"成交後全體仝人過檔談囝、架仔中撚哂伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5ab5a9d16